ON ROUTER:
Router>enable 
Router#configure 
Router(config)#clock timezone IRST 3 30
Router#clock set 16:35:10 1 jan 2026
Router#show clock 
20:5:13.932 IRST Thu Jan 1 2026
Router#clock set 13:07:10 1 jan 2026
Router#show clock 
16:37:13.983 IRST Thu Jan 1 2026
Router#configure 
Router(config)#ntp master 2
Router(config)#ntp server 194.225.150.25

ON SWITCH:
Switch>enable 
Switch#configure 
Switch(config)#ntp server 192.168.10.1
